        "\n",
        "a. $\\frac{7}{12}$\n",
        "b. $\\frac{2}{3}$\n",
        "c. $\\frac{1}{12}$\n",
        "d. $\\frac{5}{12}$\n",
        "\n",
        "::: {.callout-tip collapse=\"true\"}\n",
        "## Answer\n",
        "**a.** $P(A \\cup B) = \\frac{7}{12}$. Since $A$ and $B$ are disjoint (a marble cannot be both red and blue), $P(A \\cup B) = P(A) + P(B) = \\frac{1}{4} + \\frac{1}{3} = \\frac{3}{12} + \\frac{4}{12} = \\frac{7}{12}$.\n",
        ":::\n",
